Method Detail

getValue

public double getValue(Configuration configuration)
Default fitness for knapsack algorithm.

Returns positive number if weight if lower or equal to knapsack capacity. Returned number is price of knapsackItems in knapsack.

Returns negative number for overfilled knapsacks. Returned number is negative price of knapsackItems not in knapsack -1. (eg. if all knapsackItems are in knapsack , -1 is returned).

Specified by:
getValue in interface Fitness
Parameters:
configuration - attributes to compute fitness
Returns:
fitness of attributes
